{"tid":2025862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港共正在改寫香港歷史","createTime":"2020-05-20T14:17:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T02:23:44.000Z","uid":12554,"like":71,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"4f0f02465c43e5474c8b43f39bc58bf929736bb2","tid":2025862,"uid":12554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T14:17:16.000Z","msg":"自從上星期五出咗監狗會嘅調查報告<br />\n同埋777嘅香港的真相大背景<br />\n同埋今日出爐嘅「真相」網頁<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cn.truth-hk.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cn.truth-hk.com%2F&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krH%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=4875add6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cn.truth-hk.com/</a><br />\n港共成套組合拳就係要將過往一年嘅歷史定調同改寫<br />\n<br />\n大家可能覺得大家點會信呢啲fake news<br />\n但過多三五年呢？<br />\n海外唔係跟得咁足嘅人呢？<br />\n將來從重新研究嘅課題呢？<br />\n而家佢地一系列動作就係將fake news正名<br />\n同有系統咁紀錄<br />\n到將來就會最容易、最有系統access嘅資料就係呢一套說話<br />\n<br />\n我唔識寫database做timeline<br />\n但請各位唔出街唔送頭都唔好再鬥黃同關心網絡垃圾<br />\n香港人嘅時間真係唔多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2521d710785219db9f2c8ed3f5b9668d343f3859","tid":2025862,"uid":167394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T14:29:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"192bdef5646adcb822c15fae50ca6359e8a1c0ac","tid":2025862,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T14:31:24.000Z","msg":"我反而諗一樣嘢<br />\n大家都話自己係啱 點樣去 prove 畀人睇呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b062898aca7c5d1d65f356f5640c256b2050f983","tid":2025862,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4f0f02465c43e5474c8b43f39bc58bf929736bb2","tid":2025862,"uid":12554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"